From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: tslua-patches <patches@localhost>
Date: Thu, 17 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] ts6 migration (squashed from RealColdFry fork)

Temporary bundle of fork commits until TSTL officially migrates to TS 6.
See RealColdFry/TypeScriptToLua experiment/ts6-migration branch.
